genresAdvancedInfo.name: neo honky tonk
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A contemporary twist on the classic honky tonk sound, neo honky tonk combines traditional country instrumentation with modern production techniques. Featuring twangy guitars, honky tonk piano, and heartfelt lyrics about love, heartbreak, and the struggles of everyday life, neo honky tonk is a genre that's both nostalgic and fresh.
